Loved About:
01- Lyrics
02- Guitar Played By Ali Hamza

Hate About:
01- That Vibration in her voice
02- That Snare sounds come between really wired
03- Worst Composition by Zohaib Qazi

Suggetions:
01- Vocals Need improvments
02- She need to work on her voice alot specially the range & scale
03- Need alot practice practice & practice
